      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. so with the generator idea, is it basically just about not holding the whole thing in RAM at once? and if i'm seeing these errors, is it possible there's something else \"eating\" my memory in the background while the script runs, or is it always just the size of the objects themselves?",
